# Rust build artifacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Build-time vendored llama.cpp clone. The llama-cpp vendoring moved to
# crates/llama-cpp-sys as of the llama-cpp-sys/xybrid-llama split (#166);
# any vendor/ here is a stale pre-split build-time clone (carries its own
# .git), never source to track.
/vendor/

